WEBVTT

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:31.096
who had gone to the United States.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:35.720
They wanted the same kinds
of opportunities as my parents did.

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:37.520
I recognized them.

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.336
And so that's what we did.
We built hospitals.

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:42.176
We provided education.

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:45.616
And we did everything we could
to try to give them opportunities.

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:48.296
Now, my experience really became intense

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:51.576
at Partners in Health
in this community, Carabayllo,

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:55.440
in the northern slums of Lima, Peru.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.416
And in this community,

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:01.056
we started out by really just going
